show.description: Ek gaon ki ladki jo bas ek substitute bride banne aayi thi, lekin uske har kadam ke saath nikal rahe hain aise secrets jo sabki zindagi palat denge. Love, betrayal aur politics ke is game mein, asli dulhan kaun hai aur kiske haath lagegi jeet? To abhi dekhiye ye gripping kahani jahan har raaz ke peeche chhupa hai ek aur bada twist.
